Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Mirei isn't happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Me... happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll never happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Daybreak vs. Blackout, Nagoya Showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't care about this, do you?\NDaybreak vs. Blackout, Nagoya Showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Battle 2: Haruka vs. Megumi is finally over!\NYou don't care about this, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Battle 2: Haruka vs. Megumi is finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You could just turn off your phone.\NBattle 2: Haruka vs. Megumi is finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You could just turn off your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi has broken through Haruka, \Nthe first gatekeeper standing in their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, Blackout has broken \Nthrough the castle gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite having lost one fighter, \Nthey reach the castle's second level!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will be the next gatekeeper awaiting them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.90,0:00:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that picture book really all that interesting?\NWho will be the next gatekeeper awaiting them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposing Blackout also has \Nplenty of strong members remaining!\NIs that picture book really all that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved it when I was little.\NThe opposing Blackout also has \Nplenty of strong members remaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, you blackguards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can focus on the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.04,0:01:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's that interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...then try reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"Long ago..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.78,0:01:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"...there were..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"...two types of lions in the world:"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"Maned lions, and maneless lions."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"The maneless lions lived in the Moon Kingdom, \Na splendid and wealthy country."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:02:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"The maned lions lived in the Sun Kingdom, \Na small and poor country."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"The two countries were always fighting."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Look who's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back at my best today. Are ya sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, so I get to start by defeating you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about a shabby hors d'oeuvre!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu, don't take that twerp seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Daybreak supposed to be \Na team that prizes following rules?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd mean not getting to talk at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Masanori told me our conversation \Nwouldn't be included in the broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I can go ahead and play however I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That jerk... doesn't that mean anything goes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So hey... shall we have some fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the third fight is starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,From Daybreak, "Little Monster, \NOverflowing Malice," Shinobu Kajita! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And from the opponent Blackout, \NYu-yu Kondo comes in with fists flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Awakening of Chakrabarthi\NFlight
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Each kingdom had its own king."\NAwakening of Chakrabarthi\NFlight
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Arthur, the most cheerful of Sun Kingdom, \Nand Leon, the quietest of Moon Kingdom."\NAwakening of Chakrabarthi\NFlight
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Arthur, the most cheerful of Sun Kingdom, \Nand Leon, the quietest of Moon Kingdom."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Second to go is Yu-yu, \Nwho swiftly calls a rear-guard and attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what will Shinobu's next turn bring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With my minions' skill, I take Greedon \Nfrom my ride deck, reveal it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and draw one card.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of these kids have cute faces, \Nbut act like terrible hooligans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of us? You really don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damage check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Snerk! A wasted trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Reiyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I call Trickstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:06:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what a dignified face!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've just nonchalantly butted in, \Nonly to lose on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hear Blackout has \Njust gotten a new banner, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose, it'll get burned up again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...must not lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now all the rear-guards are deployed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The first to get them in formation is Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you wanna do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen your deck before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll crush you in the early game \Nwith one big offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A swift bombardment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu's current attack vigor is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, you got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Check me out. I'm way too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to live up to your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Avaricious Demonic Dragon, Greedon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Call in the minions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Greedon attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty, twin drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Draw trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Munch, munch, crunch, crunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hogging the attacks and all trigger effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's greed: the power to seize everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,With Greedon's skill, the minions \Nenter the Soul, and it restands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My Greedon is always, always \Nthe strongest of the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, with the minions' skill, \Nit gets an extra drive! Rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! Now you're scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gobbling up its rear-guards to restand, \Nand it even gets five total drive checks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What a greedy Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That twerp's as hideous as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,During the earlier fights...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...Shinobu never made \Na single attack with a rear-guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But Greedon restands by putting \Nfour rear-guards into the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, which means that after starting with \Nfive rear-guards, there's still one remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, Greedon makes all the attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Shinobu's unbending fighting style.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Greedon attacks once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, yeah! That's the stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this sensation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Triple drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:09:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it's like... the hunger's \Nmore insatiable than usual today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Double critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sowwy, I'm just so strong and cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Damage check.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oopsie! Now there's no way out for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn... is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu has been abruptly driven to 5 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lose, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Name 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang... that was a heck of an ending.\NYour Name 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Name 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Though both lions had been good friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,after they grew up and fought, \None of them wound up dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because both of them were kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect their kingdoms, \Nthey threw away their friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you fight and win, \Nyou can't protect your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's going to stick with \Na king who can't win, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you have to win \Nin order to achieve your goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even at the cost of ending up alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Chakrabarthi Divine Dragon, Nirvana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I must clinch the win now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Vairina overDress!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You like doing that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh, so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nirvana attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the? Aren't you gonna draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?! Don't tell me you're nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Twin drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I must draw one now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...or else lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Critical trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now a card to turn the game around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Second check!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear oh dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you perhaps expecting something dramatic, \Nlike an Over Trigger or a double critical?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu's ferocity is unflagging!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Shinobu pulls through with 5 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew, so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad for you that you couldn't end it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,After such provocation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...I refuse to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Provocation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'm talking like this to provoke you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I do it because it's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like how you guys chat \Nduring your fights at your gathering spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's how you have fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,then this is how I have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, it's not like \NI need to get you all shaken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of that strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just love that look on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then! It's about time I licked my chops!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona Ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now my Greedon won't lose until it hits 7 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget winning and losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I even get to decide who lives and who dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! A skill that increases life force!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the amount of damage Yu-yu \Nmust drive through has gone up by 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I call! And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Greedon attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With the skill of the minions \Nin the Soul, its power is 48,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I... guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scared, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"I am not scared!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two attacks remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... he doesn't have enough cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I always chow down in the tastiest, \Nmost awesome situation ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Greedon's skill activates: the minions \Nenter the Soul, and it restands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how I Cardfight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no limit to my greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Greedon demands it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to mercilessly, and relentlessly, \Nprey upon the minions before it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the proof of absolute strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, I'm the happiest and strongest ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Way too scary, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah! It does have a whole 78,000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Greedon attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:15:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you struggle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, but! Wait for it! Triple drive time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da! Heal trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now my win's clinched, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What an unbelievable Greedon fixation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A complete affront to one's self-respect, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yu-yu's turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He still needs to deal 3 damage to Shinobu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but how will he fight in this situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to deal 3 more damage to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one card in hand, and no front rear-guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... how it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You still haven't given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure I'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm afraid... of losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You were always by my side, guiding my emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Danji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...and her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are you doing at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Chakrabarthi True Dragon, Mahar Nirvana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's riding a grade 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's suddenly unclear \Nhow this match is going to end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahar Nirvana's skill activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I call Trickstar from the Drop Zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, if my opponent has 4 damage \Nor less, their Vanguard takes 1 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dealing damage without an attack?! \NCan you really do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No no no no no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't, you can't, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But... it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Vairina Valiente overDress!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahar Nirvana attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a perfect guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Triple drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek! Stop it, stop it, stop it, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,First check.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No no no no no no no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Second check!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God! Please, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Third check!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?! Wha wha whaaaa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rino gets +10,000 power and an extra critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A critical trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's over if either \Nrear-guard's attack goes through!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the?\NNow it's over if either \Nrear-guard's attack goes through!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is weird, this is weird! \NWhat damage do I lose at again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What the? What the wha the huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rino attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:19:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I guard! I guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Twist the inferno, and burn red...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fierce flame quivering, changing to wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Furious fire flourishing, let us take flight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In a blaze of crimson, transform into embers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Valiente attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With Valiente's skill, \Nbecause its attack hit, it restands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no oh oh no oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One more attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner: Yu-yu Kondo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Name 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, while it's true that he won...\NYour Name 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Name 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's kind of a lonely story, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two lions had made \Nthe effort to become good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't they have whined, "I don't want \Nto fight my friend!" and stopped the fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't be able to do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.81,0:21:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because a king... is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I'd expect from Daybreak's king. \NYour attitude is on a whole different level.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, after reading this book, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's because you're special \Nthat you're eager to be alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. I hate you. Call my brother over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. Now you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Call my brother's phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You were watching the match, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.05,0:22:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, look down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I'm useless now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.08,0:23:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You look as cool as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.67,0:23:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we lose again, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.44,0:23:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... I've grown strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.63,0:25:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.72,0:25:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Check Out My Card!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.43,0:25:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.07,0:25:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.10,0:25:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll introduce Nirvana's new form: \NChakrabarthi True Dragon, Mahar Nirvana!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.69,0:26:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For its first skill, \Nif you have a unit in overDress,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.91,0:26:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,your front row units all get +10,000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.08,0:26:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And for its second skill, when you call \Na grade 0 from the Drop Zone,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.15,0:26:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,if your opponent has 4 damage \Nor less, you give them 1 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.26,0:26:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it the... "Special Move: Trickstar Cannon!" 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.58,0:26:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Episode 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.33,0:26:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aurora Fierce Princess\NRight and Wrong 
